<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سُلَيْمَان بن دَاوُد بن وازع الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَالثَّانِي:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٢٠٣]</span> سعيد بن أبي الْحسن.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَخُو الْحسن الْبَصْرِيّ، وَاسم أَبِيه يسَار.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>